<p><b>  22</b>/&#8230;<b> Amendment to draft resolution A/HRC/22/L.13 on protecting 
 human rights defenders 
</b></p>
<p> Paragraph 9 <i>should read</i> 
</p>
<p> 9. <i>Also calls upon</i> States to ensure that reporting requirements placed on 
</p>
<p>individuals, groups and organs of society do not inhibit functional autonomy, to consider 
</p>
<p>removing<b> </b>restrictions discriminatorily imposed on potential sources of funding aimed at 
</p>
<p>supporting the work of human rights defenders, in accordance with article 29 of the 
</p>
<p>Universal Declaration of Human Rights, other than those ordinarily laid down for any other 
</p>
<p>activity unrelated to human rights within the country<b>, </b>and to ensure transparency and 
</p>
<p>accountability;  
</p>
